OL,3,CBus parade and music festival
OL,4,Cconfirmed to celebrate Coventry City's
OL,5,Cpromotion
OL,7,FCoventry City have confirmed plans to
OL,8,Fcelebrate their promotion back to the
OL,9,FPremier League with a bus parade and
OL,10,Fmusic festival.
OL,12,FThe Sky Blues needed just a point when
OL,13,Fthey took on Blackburn Rovers last
OL,14,Fnight. They went behind in the second
OL,15,Fhalf, but Bobby Thomas equalised with
OL,16,Fminutes to go to secure their
OL,17,Fpromotion back to the top flight for
OL,18,Fthe first time in 25 years.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
