OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776694272
OL,3,CBus parade and music festival
OL,4,Cconfirmed to celebrate Coventry City's
OL,5,Cpromotion
OL,7,FFollowing the game, the club has now
OL,8,Freleased information about how it
OL,9,Fplans to celebrate and mark the
OL,10,Foccasion which will all take place on
OL,11,FMonday, May 4.
OL,13,FIn a statement released just after
OL,14,Ftonight's game against Blackburn, a
OL,15,Fclub spokesman said: "Coventry City FC
OL,16,Fare delighted to announce WE ARE BACK:
OL,17,FLIVE, a city-wide celebration to mark
OL,18,Four return to the Premier League.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776694272
OL,3,CBus parade and music festival
OL,4,Cconfirmed to celebrate Coventry City's
OL,5,Cpromotion
OL,7,F"In partnership with Coventry City
OL,8,FCouncil, the city will come alive on
OL,9,FBank Holiday Monday 4 May for a bus
OL,10,Fparade and a one-day music festival in
OL,11,FWar Memorial Park for 50,000 fans.
OL,13,F"Taking place from 1pm to 7pm at the
OL,14,Ficonic War Memorial Park, the festival
OL,15,Fpromises to be an unforgettable day
OL,16,Ffor supporters of all ages and a
OL,17,Fcelebration of all things Cov.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776694272
OL,3,CBus parade and music festival
OL,4,Cconfirmed to celebrate Coventry City's
OL,5,Cpromotion
OL,7,F"Our players and management will lead
OL,8,Fan open-top bus parade through the
OL,9,Fstreets of Coventry, bringing the
OL,10,Fcelebrations direct to within the
OL,11,Fheart of our community.
OL,13,F"That parade will begin at the
OL,14,FCoventry Building Society Arena at
OL,15,F1pm, traveling through Holbrooks,
OL,16,FWhitmore Park, Keresley, Coundon and
OL,17,FChapelfields, with the parade ending
OL,18,Fat Hearsall Common."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
