OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776694272
OL,3,CBus parade and music festival
OL,4,Cconfirmed to celebrate Coventry City's
OL,5,Cpromotion
OL,7,FFor those travelling Coventry fans who
OL,8,Fmade the 260-mile round trip last
OL,9,Fnight, it marks an occasion that
OL,10,Fthey'll never forget.
OL,12,FDoug King, Coventry City owner said:
OL,13,F"Days like this are what football is
OL,14,Fall about - bringing people together
OL,15,Fto celebrate something truly special.
OL,17,F"This promotion is a huge achievement
OL,18,Ffor everyone connected to the club and
OL,19,Fthe city, and we can't wait to share
OL,20,Fit with our supporters.
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
