CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776694272
OL,3,CBus parade and music festival
OL,4,Cconfirmed to celebrate Coventry City's
OL,5,Cpromotion
OL,7,F"As a Football Club with such rich
OL,8,Fmusic culture at the heart of our DNA,
OL,9,Fit has been amazing to work alongside
OL,10,FCoventry City Council to ensure that
OL,11,Fthis great music city will have
OL,12,Fanother opportunity to showcase its
OL,13,Fvery best music talent.
OL,15,F"We're proud to give something back to
OL,16,Fthe community and make this a day
OL,17,FCoventry will never forget, and we
OL,18,Fwould like to again thank Coventry
OL,19,FCity Council for all of their support
OL,20,Fin making this event happen."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
