PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776694272
OL,3,CBus parade and music festival
OL,4,Cconfirmed to celebrate Coventry City's
OL,5,Cpromotion
OL,7,FCouncillor George Duggins, Leader of
OL,8,FCoventry City Council, also joined in
OL,9,Fthe commemorations saying it is a
OL,10,F"moment of huge significance" for the
OL,11,Fcity.
OL,13,FHe said: "This achievement belongs not
OL,14,Fonly to the team and everyone at the
OL,15,FClub, but to the supporters and
OL,16,Fcommunities who have always stood
OL,17,Fbehind them with such passion. It is a
OL,18,Fgreat time to be a Coventry City fan
OL,19,Fand for the city.
OL,26,@uD@JOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
