OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776694272
OL,3,CBus parade and music festival
OL,4,Cconfirmed to celebrate Coventry City's
OL,5,Cpromotion
OL,7,F"The celebration events on 4th May
OL,8,Fwill give the whole city the chance to
OL,9,Fcome together and share in this
OL,10,Ffantastic success.
OL,12,F"We are back and I look forward to
OL,13,Fseeing Coventry shine.
OL,15,F"This is such an amazing achievement
OL,16,Fthat I will be recommending that we
OL,17,Fcall an Extraordinary General Meeting
OL,18,Fto award the football club in its
OL,19,Fentirety, the freedom of the city.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
